{"id":"c35ccbd6-cfa4-444a-9bdb-56922fba7694","name":"Furry Frontlines RPG (100 Bot Special)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><strong>'I don't need armour dear.'</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">Battle-hardened women to take care of you, what more could you ask for?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>[Quite NSFW, Guns &amp; Stuff]</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>War's breaking through, and posters are spreading around the city.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Going on about glory, strength, and sexy anthro ladies.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Maybe joining the military won't go that badly.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>You also have some plenty of choices.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Army, Navy, Airforce...</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">And more stuff that I can't think of!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Go on soldier, prove yourself worthy.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #b5b5b5\">Of some sloppy toppy.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Related Art</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" class=\"\" style=\"\" alt=\"created by sligarthetiger\" src=\"https://static1.e621.net/data/5c/c4/5cc40d0a0568b6761b9a9795094e4ae2.png\" id=\"user-content-user-content-user-content-user-content-user-content-user-content-user-content-user-content-user-content-image\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" class=\"\" style=\"\" alt=\"arnaa created by sligarthetiger\" src=\"https://static1.e621.net/data/5c/f3/5cf3743dd56f0fb55f433adc3596b10f.png\" id=\"user-content-user-content-user-content-user-content